reviewText:
The game itself is really fun, however the netcode is terrible, shields have some issues and it appears to have a serious cheater infection.
Because of these three lacking aspects I wouldn't recommend the game. However it really is fun ... help me ;_;

EDIT: side note on my low play hours - those were from the free weekend. I have the game only on uplay now -> steam doesn't track my play time. Please be gentle.

